73,'bloc_flexible_content','a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"bloc_8\";}'),(7196,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_icon','321'),(7197,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_title','Cost management'),(7198,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_content','<h2>Cost management</h2>\r\n<h3>In an uncontrolled paper environment, unnecessary expenses are common. Plus, we often forget to factor in staff time. Make sure you know your actual printing costs.</h3>\r\nDecentralized purchasing often leads to duplicated work and unnecessary costs: larger inventories than necessary, increased losses and invoices, etc. Effectively managed purchasing is a tremendous time and money saver. Having a single supplier like Groupe CT will ensure that you manage your costs efficiently, whether you have one office or many more.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>Do you know the best methods for reducing your printing costs?</h3>\r\nPrinting technology is evolving, and so is our expertise. Grow your business by using a turnkey service that gives you a clear view of your printing costs.'),(7199,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_active','0'),(7200,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','786'),(7201,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(7202,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_icon','322'),(7203,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_title','Security and confidentiality'),(7204,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_content','<h2>Security and confidentiality</h2>\r\n<h3>Your data is the lifeblood of your organization. Do not wait to become a target.</h3>\r\nPrinting confidential documents can be a challenge. Although personal printers are a simple option, they can be unsafe. The more devices you have, the more entry points there are for hackers. We can provide you all the necessary privacy options without sacrificing the security of your infrastructure.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>Is your paper environment a risk to your company?</h3>\r\nNo company is immune to computer hacking. This is often due to vulnerabilities with respect to printing equipment. We place special emphasis on safety standards during our interventions to ensure that your business is protected.'),(7205,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_active','0'),(7206,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','787'),(7207,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(7208,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_icon','323'),(7209,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_title','Environmental footprint'),(7210,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_content','<h2>Environmental footprint</h2>\r\n<h3>Businesses are increasingly aware of the importance of environmental protection. You can make a real difference by taking the right steps to reducing your company\'s ecological footprint.</h3>\r\nSimple measures can reduce your paper and electricity consumption and waste production, thus contributing to a better future for the next generations.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>How can you reduce your environmental footprint?</h3>\r\nWe are proud to support companies throughout this process, which also allows them to develop better management of paper consumption. Ensure that your appliances meet modern environmental standards and learn how to take simple measures to reduce your impact.'),(7211,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_active','0'),(7212,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','788'),(7213,773,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(7214,773,'_edit_lock','1498931422:3'),(7215,773,'_edit_last','3'),(7216,775,'blocks','6'),(7217,775,'page_html_title','Products and<br/><span class=\"red-border\">solutions</span>'),(7218,775,'blocks_0_block','779'),(7219,775,'blocks_1_