nce. A problematic printer in a given department can become the ideal printer in another. By simply putting the devices in the right location, you can increase their lifespan and the productivity of your teams.'),(7443,785,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_icon',''),(7444,785,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_title','Sign up for<br/>our turnkey<br/>service'),(7445,785,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_description','Your business activities are your priority. Our turnkey service includes technical support, replacement parts, and ink cartridges. Take care of your printing needs by forming a unique relationship with us. It is a simple, efficient, and effective solution, whether you have many offices or only one.'),(7461,785,'_edit_lock','1499028151:1'),(7462,785,'_edit_last','1'),(7463,786,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_1_icon',''),(7464,786,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_1_title','Avoid hidden costs'),(7465,786,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_1_description','Printing costs vary depending on the printer model and the type of ink. A device that is inexpensive at the purchasing stage can lead to higher costs per copy. By associating the right device with a precise need, we can ensure the optimal distribution of printing costs.'),(7466,786,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_icon',''),(7467,786,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_title','Predict costs'),(7468,786,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_description','You can save a lot of money by predicting your costs. Take advantage of favourable rates for devices, consumables, and service by establishing use-based agreements with us. This will allow you to effectively control your costs.'),(7469,786,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_icon',''),(7470,786,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_title','Centralized<br/>purchasing'),(7471,786,'bloc_flexib