ent','<h2>Cost management</h2>\r\n<h3>Reducing printing expenses does not necessarily involve compromise. Find out what Managed Printing Services (MPS) can do for your business.</h3>\r\nPredictability of costs is one of the major advantages of an optimized paper environment. The hybrid environment provides real-time visibility and a more precise calculation of usage, allowing maximum cost control.\r\n<hr/>\r\n<h3>Do you have effective control of your printing costs?</h3>\r\nWe help you determine the factors in the printing process that affect your costs, and our experts help you keep better track and control of spending and performance, both overall and individually.'),(9056,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_active','0'),(9057,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','786'),(9058,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(9059,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_icon','322'),(9060,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_title','Security and confidentiality'),(9061,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_content','<h2>Security and confidentiality</h2>\r\n<h3>New printing technology will reduce your company\'s security issues.</h3>\r\nIn addition to the optimized paper environment, the hybrid environment allows companies to increase their level of security while having better control over their printing activities.\r\n<hr/>\r\n<h3>Does your company have an appropriate level of security?</h3>\r\nReceive advice on possible security options to achieve your print operation control goals. We will assess together the security level that suits you, from the internal user to the external user.\r\n'),(9062,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_active','0'),(9063,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','787'),(9064,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(9065,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_icon','323'),(9066,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_title','Environmental footprint'),(9067,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_content','<h2>Environmental footprint</h2>\r\n<h3>Reduce the environmental footprint of your paper document management with a better-controlled hybrid environment.</h3>\r\nThanks to the hybrid environment, you print what you really need—no more, no less. By reducing waste, you reduce your ecological footprint in a simple and effective way.\r\n<hr/>\r\n<h3>Do you know how to reduce the environmental footprint of your company without reducing efficiency? </h3>\r\nWith our expertise and range of solutions, we can help you reduce your environmental impact with solutions that help you reduce your consumption and encourage better printing habits.'),(9068,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_active','0'),(9069,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','788'),(9070,894,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(9071,894,'_edit_lock','1498937736:3'),(9072,895,'_wp_attached_file','2017/07/THEREFORE-FR.pdf'),(9073,896,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_20_wysiwyg','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Recovery of printing costs</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our solutions allow you to maximize cost control and charge costs to the right place. You can assign your printing expenses by project, department or user so as to allocate printing costs to the right place or to charge them to your clients. Our solutions allow you to produce detailed reports of these costs, according to your needs.</p>'),(9074,896,'bloc_flexible_content','a:1:{i:0;s:7:\"bloc_20\";}'),(9075,896,'_edit_lock','1498935174:4'),(9076,896,'_edit_last','4'),(9077,897,'_wp_attached_file','2017/07/THEREFORE-ET-FORMULAIRES-ÉLECTRONIQUE-FR.pdf'),(9078,898,'_wp_attached_file','2017/07/THEREFORE-DOCUSIGN.png'),(9079,898,'_wp_attachment_metada