bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_icon',''),(9092,900,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_title','Enhance the user experience'),(9093,900,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_description','Loss of time as a result of a printing problem is costly for businesses. A managed print service simplifies the user experience as well as troubleshooting, because the user can easily find his or her print jobs on another device. Printer failures need no longer affect the productivity of your teams.'),(9094,900,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_icon',''),(9095,900,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_title','Automate printing'),(9096,900,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_description','Grouping data from different systems to produce a batch of documents to send to clients takes a long time and can monopolize printing devices. A proactive solution exists to automate routine print jobs and complete them more quickly.'),(9097,900,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_icon',''),(9098,900,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_title','Reduce<br/>wait times'),(9099,900,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_description','Large jobs create a queue on the photocopier, preventing use by others. We offer solutions that allow you to share tasks across devices so that they can be completed as quickly as possible, thus reducing wait times and the number of trips to the photocopier.'),(9100,900,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row','2'),(9101,900,'bloc_flexible_content','a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"bloc_7\";}'),(9102,901,'_wp_attached_file','2017/07/THEREFORE-AND-ELECTRONIQUE-SIGNATURE-INTEGRATION-EN.pdf'),(9103,902,'blocks','2'),(9104,902,'_blocks','field_5934529e8af14'),(9105,902,'page_html_title',''),(9106,902,'_page_html_title','page_html_title_key'),(9107,902,'blocks_0_block','896'),(9108,902,'_blocks_0_block','field_593452ae8af15'),(9109,902,'blocks_1_block','887'),(9110,902,'_blocks_1_block','field