'Business efficiency'),(9686,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_0_bloc_8_content','<h2>Business efficiency</h2>\r\n<h3>The digital environment enables companies to optimize the entire lifecycle of a document from creation to destruction.</h3>\r\nDocument processing in the digital environment enables companies to increase productivity and efficiency through automated business processes that organize their document management.\r\nThe more you move into the digital environment, the greater the results.\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr/>\r\n\r\n<h3>Is your company ready to move into the digital environment?</h3>\r\nWe can help you transform your paper document management into electronic document management for more efficient handling of documents and information. By standardizing processes and facilitating communication and information sharing, your business performance will be greatly improved.'),(9687,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_0_bloc_8_active','1'),(9688,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_0_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','932'),(9689,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_0_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(9690,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse','4'),(9691,930,'bloc_flexible_content','a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"bloc_8\";}'),(9692,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_icon','321'),(9693,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_title','Cost management'),(9694,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_content','<h2>Gestion des coûts</h2>\r\n<h3>An office worker loses an average of x days a year managing paper. Generate cost savings by maximizing your employees\' time.</h3>\r\nIn a digital environment, cost savings are reflected through better employee time management. With efficient solutions, you can automate tedious processes that take up a lot of your employees’ time, so they can focus on value-added activities for your business.\r\n<hr/>\r\n<h3>Are all your operating costs justified?</h3>\r\nDifferent aspects come into play when identifying real opportunities to effectively manage your resources and costs. Time is money. We will always focus on helping you get the best return on investment.'),(9695,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_active','0'),(9696,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','934'),(9697,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_1_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(9698,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_icon','322'),(9699,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_title','Security and confidentiality'),(9700,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_content','<h2>Security and confidentiality</h2>\r\n<h3>Safeguarding information is easier in the digital environment. Give your company control of its data.</h3>\r\nElectronic document management allows you to secure your files according to rules and policies that are specific to your company. This ensures optimal, customized protection and better storage of your documents in order to preserve their legal and probative value. \r\n<hr/>\r\n<h3>Are your documents secure? How can you ensure protection and storage?</h3>\r\nWe can implement a customized solution that meets your security and protection requirements throughout the lifecycle of your documents. You will have traceability of all changes made to your electronic documents.'),(9701,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_active','0'),(9702,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','948'),(9703,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_2_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(9704,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_icon','323'),(9705,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_title','Environmental footprint'),(9706,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_content','<h2>Environmental footprint</h2>\r\n<h3>Digital environments are eco-friendly. Switch to the work environment of the future.</h3>\r\nIf a company provides the right technological tools to promote better work habits, it gradually reduces its paper consumption and therefore its environmental footprint.\r\n<hr/>\r\n<h3>Have you ever imagined working in a 100% paper-free environment?</h3>\r\nWe can help you move from a paper environment to a digital environment at your own pace, by offering modular and flexible solutions that fit your environmental needs and goals.'),(9707,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_active','0'),(9708,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_blocks_0_bloc_8_block','949'),(9709,930,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_8_collapse_3_bloc_8_blocks','1'),(9710,930,'_edit_lock','1498940264:3'),(9711,930,'_edit_last','3'),(9712,931,'blocks','3'),(9713,931,'page_html_title','Environnement<br/><span class=\"red-border\">Numérique</span>'),(9714,931,'blocks_0_block','405'),(9715,931,'blocks_1_block','407'),(9716,931,'blocks_2_block','402'),(9717,931,'_wp_page_template','default'),(9718,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_1_icon',''),(9719,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_1_title','Automate processes'),(9720,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_1_description','Some files pass through the hands of several parties, making it difficult to keep track of them. A digital environment is ideal for a clearer overview and identification of bottlenecks that slow down your processes. Through standardization, you can track the progress of each file in real time and measure your business performance.'),(9721,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_icon',''),(9722,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_title','Organize information'),(9723,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_description','Searching through disorganized information is difficult. Manual indexing seems like a good idea, but there is great risk of error. We can help you organize your information so that each document is automatically filed in the right place. A simple keyword search will be enough to find your documents, using optical character recognition (OCR).'),(9724,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_icon',''),(9725,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_title','Standardize your way of doing things'),(9726,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_description','When a company is managing several offices, information communication is a real challenge. With a digital environment, it is possible to standardize business processes and centralize the database of all your offices. File management will then be more efficient, regardless of location.'),(9727,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_icon',''),(9728,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_title','Scanning information'),(9729,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_description','One company processes thousands of invoices per year. Manually transcribing this type of data is long and involves great risk of error. We can offer you solutions that can read the information on your digital or paper documents and automatically trigger the correct type of process for each invoice.'),(9730,932,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row','2'),(9731,932,'bloc_flexible_content','a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"bloc_7\";}'),(9732,932,'_edit_lock','1498938238:3'),(9733,932,'_edit_last','3'),(9734,932,'_bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_1_icon','bloc_7_col_1_icon_key'),(9735,932,'_bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_1_title','bloc_7_col_1_title_key'),(9736,932,'_bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_1_description','bloc_7_col_1_description_key'),(9737,932,'_bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_icon','bloc_7_col_2_icon_key'),(9738,932,'_bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_title','bloc_7_col_2_title_key'),(9739,932,'_bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_description','bloc_7_col_2_description_