ses and electronic signatures.'),(9760,934,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_icon',''),(9761,934,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_title','Automate accounting processes'),(9762,934,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_description','Managing accounts payable and receivable is complicated. Late payment or billing incurs costs to the company. In a digital environment, you can automate your accounting processes so you can complete your tasks quickly and easily without neglecting the stages of approval.'),(9763,934,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_icon',''),(9764,934,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_title','Reduce storage costs'),(9765,934,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_description','The law requires a copy of certain documents to be kept for a long period. Archive boxes become full and are stored in your offices or external warehouses. Groupe CT\'s electronic document management solutions enable you to scan your documents in legal format and get rid of all paper documents, thus reducing the cost of physical storage.'),(9766,934,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row','2'),(9767,934,'bloc_flexible_content','a:2:{i:0;s:6:\"bloc_7\";i:1;s:6:\"bloc_9\";}'),(9768,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_title',''),(9769,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_1_label','7.5 hours'),(9770,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_1_primary','#063a65'),(9771,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_1_unfilled','#cdd8e0'),(9772,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_1_percentage','100'),(9773,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_1_description','<strong>7.5 hours</strong>: the average amount of time spent by an employee searching for information without finding it.'),(9774,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_1_source','AIM'),(9775,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_2_label','80%'),(9776,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_2_primary','#063a65'),(9777,934,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_9_2_unfilled','#cdd8