ist only in paper format. If there is a fire or flood, everything is lost. In your digital environment, you can ensure maximum protection for your documents and keep them safe.'),(9869,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_icon',''),(9870,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_title','Control access'),(9871,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_0_bloc_7_col_2_description','It is very difficult to manage the confidentiality of a paper document, but in a digital environment you can protect your information according to various levels of authority and manage changes and printing of documents. All actions taken with a document can be listed.'),(9872,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_icon',''),(9873,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_title','Ensure legal value'),(9874,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_1_description','“Spoke words fly away, but writing remains.” Documents are essential evidence in legal disputes. Sometimes it just takes a missing delivery note for a client to refuse to pay. With electronic document management, we can ensure that your digital archives have legal value as soon as they are created and can be used in the absence of a physical document.'),(9875,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_icon',''),(9876,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_title','Sign electronically'),(9877,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row_1_bloc_7_col_2_description','A missing signature can delay a file, and when there are several signatures to obtain, the problem multiplies. With an adequate electronic document management solution, you can use an electronic signature. We ensure you have the right electronic signature solution to meet the security standards required by law.'),(9878,948,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_7_row','2'),(9879,948,'bloc_flexible_content','a:2:{i:0;s:6:\"bloc_7\";i:1;s:6:\"bloc_9\";}'),(9880,948,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc