at\'s CT!\r\n \r\nWe are more than ever ready to accompany you on your digital journey. Are you?'),(10987,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_cta_label',''),(10988,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_cta_link',''),(10989,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_cta_blank','0'),(10990,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_cta_open_contact','0'),(10991,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_phone_1_location',''),(10992,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_phone_1_label',''),(10993,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_phone_1',''),(10994,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_phone_2_location',''),(10995,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_phone_2_label',''),(10996,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_phone_2',''),(10997,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_image','252'),(10998,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_3_image_left','1'),(10999,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_5_slide_0_bloc_5_slide_image','252'),(11000,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_5_slide_0_bloc_5_slide_testimonial',' \r\n« En 30 ans d’expérience, nous avons vu le marché se transformer et, à l’ère où nous évoluons aujourd’hui, nous connaissons les enjeux liés à la productivité des entreprises. Nous nous démarquons par notre approche-conseil audacieuse et notre offre de solutions intégrées qui simplifient la gestion documentaire.»\r\n“In 30 years of experience, we have seen the market transform and we know the issues relating to company productivity in our current climate. We stand out by our bold consulting approach and our offering of integrated solutions that simplify document management.”\r\n'),(11001,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_5_slide_0_bloc_5_slide_author','Tommy Bélanger'),(11002,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_5_slide_0_bloc_5_slide_author_title','President, Groupe CT'),(11003,1014,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_5_slide','1'),(11004,1014,'_edit_lock','1498946624:3'),(11005,1014,'_edit_last','3'),(11006,1015,'_wp_attached_file','2017/06/union-bgd.png'),(11007,1015,'_wp_attachment_metadata',