 values, there was no doubt that the merger of BGD and SAC would be a success.\r\n \r\nSince February 2017, Bureautique Guy Drouin has become Solutions d’Affaires de la Capitale, which continues to develop with the same strong values that have earned the whole group its reputation: close proximity, respect and the quest for excellence.'),(11098,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_1_cta_label','See our press release'),(11099,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_1_cta_link','#'),(11100,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_1_cta_blank','0'),(11101,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_2_title',''),(11102,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_2_description',''),(11103,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_2_cta_label',''),(11104,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_2_cta_link',''),(11105,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_2_cta_blank','0'),(11106,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_3_title',''),(11107,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_3_description',''),(11108,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_3_cta_label',''),(11109,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_3_cta_link',''),(11110,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_3_cta_blank','0'),(11111,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_2_icon',''),(11112,1020,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_6_3_icon',''),(11113,1020,'_edit_lock','1498947243:3'),(11114,1020,'_edit_last','3'),(11115,1021,'_wp_attached_file','2017/06/BGD-petit.png'),(11116,1021,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:580;s:6:\"height\";i:370;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"2017/06/BGD-petit.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:4:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"BGD-petit-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"BGD-petit-300x191.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:191;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:15:\"_themosis_media\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"BGD-petit-100x100.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:100;s:6:\"height\";i:100;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:8:\"themosis\";a:4:{