d itself as one of the industry\'s largest players in Canada.'),(11276,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_19_center_description','1'),(11277,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_2_bloc_16_timeline_order','ASC'),(11278,1036,'bloc_flexible_content','a:4:{i:0;s:7:\"bloc_19\";i:1;s:7:\"bloc_19\";i:2;s:7:\"bloc_16\";i:3;s:7:\"bloc_20\";}'),(11279,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_3_bloc_20_wysiwyg','<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Groupe CT’s success has not been achieved alone: it is the result of efforts by our employees who, over time, have been able to adapt and innovate alongside market needs. It is this culture of change that allows us to offer the best to our clients.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Learn more about our expertise and approach to document management.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"btn primary-btn-blue\" href=\"/approche-conseil/\">Notre Approche</a></p>'),(11280,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_19_subheader',''),(11281,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_19_subheader_carret','0'),(11282,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_19_center_subheader','0'),(11283,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_19_title','A history that makes us proud'),(11284,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_19_center_title','1'),(11285,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_19_description','Groupe CT was founded in Laval and has been operating in the printing technology industry for over 30 years. Over the years, we have helped thousands of companies increase their productivity and efficiency by providing state-of-the-art equipment that is adapted to their needs.\r\n \r\nWith the arrival of Tomy Bélanger in 2008, the company gained new momentum. Groupe CT has earned the trust of several major Canadian companies through its unique approach. In eight years, the turnover has multiplied by 20, even though it is a mature industry. Recognized several times as Canada\'s largest Canon retailer, the company is now a consolidator and seeks to expand its expertise across Canada.\r\n \r\nAlways on the lookout for new trends, the company is moving into digital! Groupe CT is looking to the future by offering innovative electronic document management solutions to help companies move to a paperless environment.'),(11286,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_19_center_description','1'),(11287,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_block_19_background_color','#f6f6f6'),(11288,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_1_block_19_background_color',''),(11289,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_19_remove_padding','0'),(11290,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_0_bloc_19_remove_margin','0'),(11291,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_19_remove_padding','0'),(11292,1036,'bloc_flexible_content_1_bloc_19_remove_margin','0'),(11293,1036,'_edit_lock','1498948920:3'),(11294,1036,'_edit_last','3'),(11297,1037,'post_show_date','1'),(11298,1037,'_post_show_date','post_show_date_key'),(11299,1037,'post_is_featured','1'),(11300,1037,'_post_is_featured','post_is_featured_key'),(11301,1037,'post_featured_image',''),(11302,1037,'_post_featured_image','post_featured_image_key'),(11303,1037,'post_standard_image',''),(11304,1037,'_post_standard_image','post_standard_image_key'),(11306,1038,'post_show_date','1'),(11307,1038,'_post_show_date','post_show_date_key'),(11308,1038,'post_is_featured','1'),(11309,1038,'_post_is_featured','post_is_featured_key'),(11310,1038,'post_featured_image',''),(11311,1038,'_post_featured_image','post_featured_image_key'),(11312,1038,'post_standard_image',''),(11313,1038,'_post_standard_image','post_standard_image_key'),(11315,1039,'post_show_date','1'),(11316,1039,'_post_show_date','post_show_date_key'),(11317,1039,'post_is_featured','1'),(11318,1039,'_post_is_featured','post_is_featured_key'),(11319,1039,'post_featured_image',''),(11320,1039,'_post_featured_image','post_featured_image_key'),(11321,1039,'post_standard_image','1033'),(11322,1039,'_post_standard_image','post_standard_image_key'),(11324,1040,'post_show_date','1'),(11325,1040,'_post_show_date','post_show_date_key'),(