55:08','<h3><b>Groupe CT and the Montreal Alouettes</b></h3>\r\nGroupe CT is proud to announce that it became the Montreal Alouettes’ official partner for all needs that are related to document management.\r\n\r\nGroupe CT will provide reliable, high-performance printing devices, as well as effective technical support. The company will allow the Montreal Alouettes to focus on its main goal, winning football games! That being said, Groupe CT is delighted to contribute to the success of this team, that is a source of Montreal’s pride.\r\n<h3><b>About Groupe CT</b></h3>\r\nIn business since 1987, Groupe CT has experienced one of the largest growth in the printing technology industry. Groupe CT helps companies optimize their paper environment through digital document management. Regardless of where a company stands in its digital path, Groupe CT accompanies it in the entire implementation. First, by offering state-of-the-art printing devices and then, by integrating software that adds Managed Print Services (GIS) and Electronic Document Management (EDM) tailored to the company’s workflow.\r\n<h3><b>About the Montreal Alouettes</b></h3>\r\nEvolving from a rich history, the Montreal Alouettes football team was founded in 1946. This organization has won the Canadian Football League\'s supremacy emblem, the Grey Cup, seven times since 1949. The local games are held at the Percival-Molson Memorial Stadium, situated on the south-east side of Montreal’s beautiful Mount Royal .','GROUPE CT BECOMES THE OFFICIAL PARTNER OF THE MONTREAL ALOUETTES','','publish','open','open','','groupe-ct-becomes-the-official-partner-of-the-montreal-alouettes','','','2017-07-01 22:11:40','2017-07-01 22:11:40','',0,'https://groupect.staging.ctrlweb.ca/?p=721',0,'post','',0),(722,2,'2017-06-29 19:55:08','2017-06-29 19:55:08','<h3><b>Groupe CT and the Montreal Alouettes</b></h3>\r\nGroupe CT is proud to announce that it became the Montreal Alouettes’ official partner for all needs that are related to 